---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Digital Marketing for E-Commerce" description="Specialist e-commerce digital marketing: Google Shopping, Performance Max, Meta catalogue ads, affiliate programmes, and Shopify builds. Spires Digital, Guernsey &amp; Lichfield.">
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Industries', href: '/industries/ecommerce' }, { label: 'E-Commerce' }]} />

  <section class="page-hero" style="margin-top: -2rem;">
    <div class="container page-hero-content">
      <span class="badge">E-Commerce Marketing</span>
      <h1>Digital Marketing for E-Commerce Brands</h1>
      <p>Revenue-focused strategies that turn browsers into buyers. From Google Shopping to Meta catalogue ads, we help e-commerce businesses scale profitably with data-driven campaigns.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <h2>The E-Commerce Marketing Challenge</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Selling online is more competitive than ever. If any of these sound familiar, you're not alone.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="icon-box">🛒</div>
          <h3>Rising Acquisition Costs</h3>
          <p>CPCs are climbing across Google and Meta. Without tight campaign management and feed optimisation, your margins shrink with every click.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="icon-box">📉</div>
          <h3>Low Conversion Rates</h3>
          <p>Traffic without conversions is just an expense. Many e-commerce brands struggle with checkout abandonment, poor product pages, and weak retargeting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="icon-box">🔄</div>
          <h3>Channel Fragmentation</h3>
          <p>Google Shopping, Meta, affiliate networks, email — managing multiple channels without a unified strategy leads to wasted spend and missed opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="icon-box">📊</div>
          <h3>Attribution Confusion</h3>
          <p>With iOS privacy changes and cross-device journeys, understanding which channels actually drive revenue is harder than ever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Approach -->
      <h2>Our Approach to E-Commerce Growth</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 2rem;">We combine paid media expertise with deep e-commerce understanding to build campaigns that scale profitably.</p>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">1</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Revenue Audit</h3>
            <p>We analyse your product data, margins, and current campaign performance to identify the highest-value opportunities and quick wins.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">2</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Feed &amp; Catalogue Optimisation</h3>
            <p>Your product feed is the foundation of Shopping and catalogue campaigns. We optimise titles, descriptions, images, and custom labels for maximum visibility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">3</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Multi-Channel Campaigns</h3>
            <p>Coordinated campaigns across Google Shopping, Performance Max, Meta catalogue ads, and affiliate networks — all working towards the same revenue targets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">4</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Test, Measure &amp; Scale</h3>
            <p>Continuous A/B testing of creatives, audiences, and bidding strategies. We double down on what works and cut what doesn't.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tip-box" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <strong>Pro tip:</strong> E-commerce brands that combine Google Shopping with Meta retargeting typically see 30–50% higher ROAS than those relying on a single channel.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services for E-Commerce -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <h2>Services for E-Commerce Brands</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Every service we offer is tailored to the unique demands of online retail.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <a href="/services/ppc-management" class="service-link-card">
          <h3>Google Shopping &amp; PPC</h3>
          <p>Search campaigns, Shopping feeds, and Performance Max — all managed to maximise your return on ad spend.</p>
          <span class="link-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/meta-ads" class="service-link-card">
          <h3>Meta Catalogue Ads</h3>
          <p>Dynamic product ads across Facebook and Instagram that retarget browsers and drive repeat purchases.</p>
          <span class="link-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/affiliate-management" class="service-link-card">
          <h3>Affiliate Programme Management</h3>
          <p>Recruit, manage, and optimise affiliate partners to create a profitable, performance-based sales channel.</p>
          <span class="link-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/shopify-builds" class="service-link-card">
          <h3>Shopify Store Builds</h3>
          <p>Conversion-optimised Shopify stores built from the ground up, or existing store redesigns to improve performance.</p>
          <span class="link-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats / Results -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <h2 style="text-align: center;">Results We Deliver for E-Commerce</h2>
      <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Average performance improvements across our e-commerce client portfolio.</p>
      <div class="stat-grid">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-value">340%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Average ROAS</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-value">+62%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Conversion Rate Lift</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-value">-38%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Cost Per Acquisition</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-value">+85%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Revenue Growth (Avg.)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How much should an e-commerce brand spend on digital advertising?</summary>
          <p>There's no one-size-fits-all answer, but most successful e-commerce brands invest 10–20% of revenue back into advertising. We'll help you determine the right budget based on your margins, average order value, and growth goals.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you manage Google Shopping and Performance Max campaigns?</summary>
          <p>Absolutely. Google Shopping and Performance Max are core to our e-commerce offering. We handle everything from product feed optimisation and campaign structure to bid management and ongoing performance tuning.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can you help with Shopify store setup as well as marketing?</summary>
          <p>Yes — we offer end-to-end Shopify builds alongside our marketing services. Having one team handle both ensures your store is built for conversions from day one, with proper tracking, landing pages, and product page optimisation.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How do you track ROI across multiple channels?</summary>
          <p>We implement comprehensive conversion tracking through GA4 and platform-specific pixels, alongside server-side tracking where needed. Monthly reports clearly show revenue, ROAS, and cost per acquisition for each channel.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What makes your approach different from other e-commerce agencies?</summary>
          <p>We focus on profit, not just revenue. Every campaign decision is rooted in your actual margins and business economics. We also offer full transparency — you own all accounts and data, and we report on the metrics that matter to your bottom line.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Scale Your E-Commerce Revenue?</h2>
      <p>Get a free audit of your current campaigns and discover untapped growth opportunities.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Get Your Free Audit</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How much should an e-commerce brand spend on digital advertising?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "There's no one-size-fits-all answer, but most successful e-commerce brands invest 10–20% of revenue back into advertising. We'll help you determine the right budget based on your margins, average order value, and growth goals."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do you manage Google Shopping and Performance Max campaigns?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Absolutely. Google Shopping and Performance Max are core to our e-commerce offering. We handle everything from product feed optimisation and campaign structure to bid management and ongoing performance tuning."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can you help with Shopify store setup as well as marketing?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes — we offer end-to-end Shopify builds alongside our marketing services. Having one team handle both ensures your store is built for conversions from day one, with proper tracking, landing pages, and product page optimisation."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How do you track ROI across multiple channels?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "We implement comprehensive conversion tracking through GA4 and platform-specific pixels, alongside server-side tracking where needed. Monthly reports clearly show revenue, ROAS, and cost per acquisition for each channel."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What makes your approach different from other e-commerce agencies?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "We focus on profit, not just revenue. Every campaign decision is rooted in your actual margins and business economics. We also offer full transparency — you own all accounts and data, and we report on the metrics that matter to your bottom line."
        }
      }
    ]
  })} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .challenge-card { padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-radius: var(--radius); }
  .challenge-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .challenge-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  .process-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; align-items: start; }
  .step-num { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-accent); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .step h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .step p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  .service-link-card { display: block; padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--color-white); border-radius: var(--radius); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); transition: all var(--transition); text-decoration: none; }
  .service-link-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); border-color: var(--color-accent); }
  .service-link-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .service-link-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .link-arrow { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-accent); }
  .faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .faq-item { background: var(--color-white); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); overflow: hidden; }
  .faq-item summary { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item summary::after { content: '+'; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 1rem; }
  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '−'; }
  .faq-item p { padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
</style>
